Thanks to @[Nate Barbettini][1]&#39;s answer for steering me in the right direction on this.

Also, it appears that AES ECB mode does **not require** an initialisation vector unlike other
modes like CBC so I didn&#39;t specify an IV.

For padding I specified PKCS7 (again thanks to @[Nate Barbettini][1] for that).

